# The Famous Cases
## Pluto
Pluto was: 
-> Orbiting the sun (though Charon was a nuisance)
-> Approximately round
-> But did not clear its neighbourhood. It is present in the Kuiper belt, surrounded by hundreds of smaller objects.
Hence it is not a planet but a dwarf planet. (Demotion)
## Ceres
Ceres was:
-> Orbiting the Sun
-> Approximately Round
-> But did not clear its neighbourhood. It is in the Asteroid belt. 
Hence it is not an asteroid but a dwarf planet. (Promotion)
